@jolielaide1608 Have mixed coconut milk in the rice. Should have drizzled some on the mango 🙈
Wow!Home made mango with sticky rice😍😍😍😍Without coconuts milk?
The way you’ve cut the mango makes all the difference! 👌🏼
Wow like fine dining dessert style! 👍👍👏
@yvonnemsw By special, I mean in a good way 😊
You mango sticky rice so special!
@vnm_lee I love your blue pea version more, so beautiful 😍
@yvonnemsw This is still tempting delicious n looks so pretty!!!! 😍😍❤️❤️
@yvonnemsw This is still tempting delicious n very pretty!!!! 😍😍❤️❤️
My favourite dessert, oh that mango must be so so sweet!! And this is so Sui!! 😍
My all time fave! I think during circuit breaker everyone should indulge themselves. Dessert for lunch sound great😍😋👌🥭
@foodie_homechef Prefer your Mango rose, I didn't manage to shape it 😆
Aweaome.. looks so pretty and inviting🤗😍
